T1  - Classification for Market Segmentation: An Improved Linear Model for Solving Problems of Arbitrary Origin
AU  - Darden, William R.
AU  - Perreault, William D.
Y1  - 1977/11/01
PY  - 1977
DA  - 1977/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.24.3.259
